I"S<p><strong>Medium fiend (devil), lawful evil</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 13 (natural armor)</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 52 (8d8+16)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 30 ft.</p>

